{"comments":"Card Badge — Overlay badges, tags, and labels for cards.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nBadges are positioned overlays that communicate status, price, category,\nor other metadata. They can be placed at corners or edges.\n\n## Badge Types\n\n- **Status**: \"NEW\", \"SALE\", \"SOLD OUT\", \"HOT\"\n- **Price**: \"$19.99\", \"From $5\"\n- **Rating**: \"4.5 ★\"\n- **Category**: \"Electronics\", \"Fashion\"\n- **Custom**: Any text/icon combination\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- E-commerce product cards (price, sale badge)\n- Etsy/Amazon-style UGC cards\n- Article cards (category tag)\n- Profile cards (online status)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Schema.Color.RGB (badge colors)\n- Schema.Typography (text styling)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[90,3]},"title":"BadgeTopLeft"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[91,3]},"title":"BadgeTopRight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[92,3]},"title":"BadgeBottomLeft"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[93,3]},"title":"BadgeBottomRight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[94,3]},"title":"BadgeTopCenter"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[95,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Card/Badge.purs","start":[95,3]},"title":"BadgeBottomCent